{"tid":681850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不是梁天琦，沒人關注，幫手　請不要消費旺角義士　可找星火同盟　送信送餅送煙及捐助","createTime":"2018-05-28T11:26:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T03:48:13.000Z","uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4bc346e0b93dd69551086bd7d1af8407e7df3f7d","tid":681850,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T11:26:23.000Z","msg":"想關注各位旺角義士最新消息同動態　請follow星火同盟抗爭支援page<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sparkalliancehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsparkalliancehk%2F&d=Ss2A3sSqX1HWH8GxpL3HcG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=b5b65e6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sparkalliancehk/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有咩想幫助義士　可以 pm 星火o既專頁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n星火o既亦都有各種有關義士o既訊息<br />\n<br />\n有組織籌款支援在囚或審訊中義士　星火專頁亦會些牙<br />\n<br />\n星火亦有各種活動聲援義士　例如o岩o岩星期日o係金鐘擺攤寫心意卡<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sparkalliancehk/photos/a.1989972677956521.1073741829.1965117443775378/2140801336206987/?type=3&amp;permPage=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsparkalliancehk%2Fphotos%2Fa.1989972677956521.1073741829.1965117443775378%2F2140801336206987%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26permPage%3D1&d=Ss2A3sSqX1HWH8GxpL3HcG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=025d5c0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sparkalliancehk/photos/a.1989972677956521.1073741829.1965117443775378/2140801336206987/?type=3&amp;permPage=1</a><br />\n<br />\n3月17日<br />\n<br />\n【義士抱恙暈倒】<br />\n<br />\n於旺角衝突 5人案中被控暴動罪的義士發仔，早前疑因氣溫驟降，在獄中工作時不支暈倒送院，現時情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n在此我們呼籲市民，注意天氣變化，保重身體；亦希望大家多多關心服刑中的發仔 &mdash; 身陷囹圄的他極需大家為他送上支持與祝福，陪伴他直至康復過來。<br />\n<br />\n大家若有寫給發仔的書信，敬請 PM 本專頁或寄往尖沙咀郵政信箱98529號，信面註明發仔收，我們將以最快速度將大家的信件轉交發仔。先感謝大家對他的關心！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/uMmp1r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FuMmp1r&h=02bf29aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e308058b34c5b1c1ae094628ac28d7f341a0e4f8","tid":681850,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T09:42:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aab606c25af334785a1335d0ca4fc364cf22a904","tid":681850,"uid":129139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:48:13.000Z","msg":"【連登革命宣言！】向殖民政權下戰書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1203758\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1203758</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n麻煩各位將個宣言周圍 share，<br />\n解釋行動者理念。海外人士可以的話，<br />\n用英文簡單總結行動理念，send 去各大媒體：<br />\n行動者絕對唔係盲目崇尚暴力。"}]}